Package de.uni_mannheim.informatik.dws.winter.datafusion Description

Package for Data Fusion. Contains the DataFusionEngine and pre-implemented conflict resolution functions. To run data fusion, you must define a DataFusionStrategy and run it with the DataFusionEngine
